{"tid":1790963,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[行動]元朗恐襲五個月 黨鐵商場和你坐","createTime":"2019-12-20T11:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T08:20:07.000Z","uid":94771,"like":50,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"86be49b90ca6fe3a041a3c2d4bf3f2ebda5471b5","tid":1790963,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oOFoqFp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoOFoqFp.jpg&h=112bbecc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ok1ror5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fok1ror5.jpg&h=7c9b9214&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原POST，幫手重開新，容易上熱門<br />\n[長期置頂]元朗恐襲五個月 黨鐵商場和你坐<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1785918\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1785918</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今個星期六就係元朗恐襲五個月</span><br />\n<br />\n銀髮集會個主題唔係追究721都有人推 反而無人推五個月行動？<br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你哋係唔係唔記得晒嗰日發生咩事 香港人係唔係咁撚善忘呀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n小弟有一個行動想分享吓<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">夠一千正評就唔該同我全世界做文宣</span><br />\n<br />\n時間：1500<br />\n地點：元朗yoho mall <br />\n行動細節：主題 追究721事件 做聖誕文宣 邀請人入工會 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果黨鐵一如概往噉封站 就全世界同我去 <br />\n<br />\n圓方（黨鐵）<br />\n連城廣場（黨鐵）<br />\nPopcorn(shk)<br />\nV city(shk)<br />\nIFC(shk)<br />\n荃灣廣場（shk)<br />\nyoho mall(shk,元朗人限定，提前閂就可以走去其他度幫手）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n主要喺元朗搞 但如果提前封站 次次都聚唔到人 結果元朗因為唔夠人 搞到好多手足被捕 其他手足又唔知可以點 所以我而家揀嘅地點都好近黨鐵 行動要可以吸引和理非參與 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">只要夠多人 就可以唔洗犧牲手足都達至經濟攬炒</span><br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你哋係唔係重要靠勇武手足幫你哋犧牲呀 可唔可以變咗係和理非保護返勇武手足呀 </span><br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">所以大家一定要做好文宣 1221我要見到你哋咁多個</span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>勿忘721<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"dc6579366521cf0b3c571173701ae7df13f83080","tid":1790963,"uid":1891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:34:21.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n1221<br />\n721後嘅五個月<br />\n香港人有忘記嗎？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UPEkp4G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUPEkp4G.jpg&h=82652877&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c29b11faa6e8fca55dafa6b8efd4b81f746e27ac","tid":1790963,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:44:11.000Z","msg":"推！！"},{"pid":"c63298e03ec9f2ce3c6d3884bd5a7f29b2e393a2","tid":1790963,"uid":115069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:46:02.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"9880d6ac04d5056ec6ec2f16eec36f41a9952a45","tid":1790963,"uid":115069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T11:46:57.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"a2512e26590363462b47d51c3911705c743c7d74","tid":1790963,"uid":139156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T12:15:57.000Z","msg":"1點封站<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KTQS3GB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKTQS3GB.png&h=fb9c121e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3100b214ec69f53f1aa9bd60de1babb16a7f5ae8","tid":1790963,"uid":223208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T12:16:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0e9677818a1ef112c5f9477b8fd267ec5cd1035","tid":1790963,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T12:41:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94f7d5578f82d8af2b2def395472110275e8e670","tid":1790963,"uid":4838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T12:43:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1dea821a11d15c303053a623801eb99878e93dd5","tid":1790963,"uid":141097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T12:46:55.000Z","msg":"<img 